io.appium.java_client.pagefactory

Annotation Type SelendroidFindBy


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value={FIELD,TYPE})
public @interface SelendroidFindBy
    Used to mark a field on a Page Object to indicate an alternative mechanism for locating the element or a list of elements. Used in conjunction with PageFactory this allows users to quickly and easily create PageObjects. using Selendroid UI selectors like, id, name, class name, tag and xpath

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String className
      It is a className of the target element.
      String id
      It is an id of the target element.
      String linkText
      It is a text of the desired element.
      String name
      It is used in Selendroid mode instead of accessibility id.
      String partialLinkText
      It is a part of the text of the desired element.
      String tagName
      It is a desired element tag.
      String xpath
      It is a xpath to the target element.
